一直是我的。”他说。 “各种各样的叔叔。在我的核心中，埃里克·莫雷卡姆（Eric Morecambe）的精神为我的灵魂提供了反感。埃里克（Eric）让我感到的感觉是我想让人们的感觉。只要想到它们，才能创造出如此喜悦的礼物，并让他们看到快乐。”</p><p> Over 800 items were auctioned, including a 1978 portrait of Morecambe by the artist Richard Stone, which went for £15,000, and his ventriloquist dummy Charlie which sold for £6,200 – twice its highest estimate.</p><p> Elsewhere bidders picked up a letter from Wise to Morecambe which revealed he wished to end their partnership for £3,200, his tailcoat and trousers from the Morecambe and Wise Show for £4,500 and a vintage Luton Town FC tracksuit with Eric stitched on the back for £5,500. </p><figure id="attachment_3828743" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828743" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828743" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Robbie Williams in New York City, January 2025" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Robbie-williams@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828743" class="wp-caption-text"> Robbie Williams in New York City, January 2025. CREDIT: MEGA/GC Images</figcaption></figure><p> In other Robbie Williams news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-scores-15th-number-one-album-with-better-man-soundtrack-now-equal-with-the-beatles-record-3831879">the singer recently secured his 15th Number One album</a> with the <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/better-man-review-robbie-williams-strangest-music-biopic-3807590"><em>Better Man</em></a> soundtrack, which has tied him with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/The-Beatles">The Beatles</a> .</p><p> Williams currently holds the record as the solo artist with the most UK Number One albums. Now, with his 15th Number One record, he is in the same range as The Beatles&#39; record.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/better-man-review-robbie-williams-strangest-music-biopic-3807590">In a three-star review of Williams&#39; biopic</a> – which was directed by Michael Gracey ( <em>The Greatest Showman</em> ) and sees the singer depicted as a CGI monkey and tells his life story – <em>NME</em> shared: “This is &#39;Rudebox&#39; on film: some of it good, some of it very bad, all of it a bit of a mess.尽管如此，猴子音乐剧还是没有其他人会带来的大摇摆。 You can&#39;t fault the chutzpah or the ambition. If it makes back its reported budget, we&#39;ll eat $110m worth of bananas.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-bought-uncle-of-sorts-eric-morecambes-iconic-glasses-and-pipe-at-auction-for-20k-3836315">Robbie Williams bought “uncle of sorts” Eric Morecambe&#39;s iconic glasses and pipe at auction for £20k</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
